        {
            "title": "商湯半年虧損收窄40% 不派息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">商湯(00020)公布截至6月30日非國際財務報告準則經調整虧損淨額11.62億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年收窄50%，虧損14.87億元，按年收窄39.9%。不派息。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">收入23.58億元，按年升35.6%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：商湯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_00020-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：商湯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_00020-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：商湯官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">經調整EBITDA為虧損5.21億元，按年收窄72.5%。EBITDA為虧損8.47億元，按年收窄58.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">毛利率38.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">貿易應收回款額31.59億元，按年提升95.5%，公司稱，體現銷售與交付閉環效率顯著加快。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截止2025年6月30日現金儲備為131.584億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生成式AI收入18.16億元，同比增長72.7%，對集團貢獻佔比提升至77%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15213231-%e5%95%86%e6%b9%af%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%8440-%e4%b8%8d%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240606_FI_source-web_00020-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-28 18:40:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
